, caching, and streaming; no Docker service is needed.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The existing 5.0.0 build.gradle applies the Netty/JDK25 runtime properties only when `libraryVersion == '5.0.0'`; running the same scaffold with `GVM_TCK_LV=5.0.1` can drop those properties and fail native runtime.\",\n    \"OAuth2-specific WebClient APIs reference optional `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2`; avoid making OAuth2 coverage mandatory unless the workflow deliberately adds that optional dependency.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c762e14780d5003016a3e79e0baac8197a72f322cd43ae65f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1437, "output": 770, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23199, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782479319946, "responseId": "resp_0c762e14780d5003016a3e79d868b4819794b9f072f9e51c79"}}
